# HeatShield-IoT

### Smart IoT-Based Heatwave Protection System

An intelligent wearable healthcare and cooling platform designed to protect people from heatwaves through real-time health monitoring, automatic cooling, and proactive heatstroke prevention.

---

## About The Project

HeatShield-IoT is designed to address the growing threat of extreme heatwaves, which pose serious health risks to outdoor workers, elderly individuals, athletes, and people living in hot climates.

Traditional wearable devices can monitor health conditions but cannot actively protect users from heat stress. Similarly, cooling devices provide temporary comfort but lack intelligent health monitoring capabilities.

HeatShield-IoT combines both functionalities into a unified wearable ecosystem consisting of:

* Smart Health Monitoring Band
* Smart Neck Cooling Gadget

The system continuously monitors physiological and environmental parameters and automatically activates cooling when heat stress conditions are detected.

---

## Why HeatShield-IoT?

Heatwaves can cause:

* Dehydration
* Heat exhaustion
* Fatigue
* Reduced productivity
* Life-threatening heatstroke

Current solutions either monitor health or provide cooling, but very few offer both in an integrated and intelligent manner.

HeatShield-IoT addresses these challenges by combining:

* Real-time health monitoring
* Intelligent heat stress detection
* Automatic thermoelectric cooling
* IoT connectivity
* Emergency alert mechanisms

This creates a proactive and wearable safety solution capable of protecting users before critical conditions occur.

